01:59:24.438 --> 01:59:27.658
This industry-friendly framing needs to be examined, because we have seen this

2250
01:59:27.678 --> 01:59:31.298
tactic before in other sectors that also profit from harmful

2251
01:59:31.358 --> 01:59:34.958
products. They're quick to lead with the benefits and happy to

