01:59:35.018 --> 01:59:35.878
omit or

2253
01:59:37.298 --> 01:59:40.878
downgrade the costs, but when those costs are the health and well-being of our

2254
01:59:40.918 --> 01:59:43.718
whānau, of our communities, then we have a responsibility to speak up.

2255
01:59:45.088 --> 01:59:48.798
For decades, Māori have carried the heaviest burden of alcohol harm in

2256
01:59:48.838 --> 01:59:52.738
Aotearoa. We see that harm in our hospitals, in our homes, and

2257
01:59:52.778 --> 01:59:55.028
in the preventable loss of Māori lives.

2258
01:59:56.178 --> 01:59:59.638
One in four Māori are classified as hazardous drinkers,

2259
02:00:00.478 --> 02:00:04.218
and too often the alcohol harm is framed as

2260
02:00:05.238 --> 02:00:06.198
poor individual choice,

2261
02:00:07.218 --> 02:00:10.138
while the systems and policies that drive the harm are ignored.

2262
02:00:10.738 --> 02:00:14.658
For too long, these systems have prioritized industry interests over the well-being

2263
02:00:14.718 --> 02:00:18.658
of whānau and communities. We see this in targeted marketing

2264
02:00:18.738 --> 02:00:22.518
and alcohol licenses granted with little regard for local

2265
02:00:22.558 --> 02:00:25.638
context, and in the saturation of outlets across our

2266
02:00:25.678 --> 02:00:29.578
communities. Communities that are already at breaking point and less able

2267
02:00:29.618 --> 02:00:30.468
to take any more.

2268
02:00:31.978 --> 02:00:34.018
We have several key concerns with this bill.

2269
02:00:34.938 --> 02:00:35.278
First,

2270
02:00:36.458 --> 02:00:39.898
loosening restrictions and increasing access to alcohol sends the wrong message to

2271
02:00:39.918 --> 02:00:41.458
our communities, especially our rangatahi.

2272
02:00:42.018 --> 02:00:45.838
It will further normalize alcohol in everyday life when we should be

2273
02:00:45.878 --> 02:00:46.598
doing the opposite.

2274
02:00:47.718 --> 02:00:51.348
Second, this bill risks increasing the number of outlets in our communities,

2275
02:00:51.898 --> 02:00:53.998
and we know the evidence is clear here.

2276
02:00:54.598 --> 02:00:58.438
Greater availability leads to greater harm, so more

2277
