02:02:03.328 --> 02:02:06.678
The relationship between availability, affordability, and

2298
02:02:06.738 --> 02:02:08.638
alcohol-related harm is well-established,

2299
02:02:09.538 --> 02:02:13.238
yet this bill in its current form reflects industry preference over public health

