2302
02:02:22.378 --> 02:02:25.278
They're looking for fewer bottle stores, safer streets, strong protections for

2303
02:02:25.378 --> 02:02:25.828
rangatahi,

2304
02:02:26.738 --> 02:02:30.714
communities that are free from the harms caused by alcohol.And

2305
02:02:30.894 --> 02:02:34.374
this bill, once again, in its current form ignores those voices.

2306
02:02:35.494 --> 02:02:37.994
When we talk about policy, we're talking about real people, real whanau, and real

2307
02:02:38.054 --> 02:02:41.534
communities affected by the decisions made in this room.

2308
02:02:42.954 --> 02:02:45.834
And because of this, our position is clear that this bill should not pass in its

