access, and explicitly recognizing te tiriti in the

2315
02:03:06.394 --> 02:03:08.294
legislation.

2316
02:03:09.114 --> 02:03:12.594
We are not asking for perfection, and we certainly are not demanding prohibition,

2317
02:03:12.834 --> 02:03:16.714
but we are asking for courage because the status quo, business

2318
02:03:16.754 --> 02:03:19.754
